 * This routine converts time as follows.
 * The epoch is 0000 Jan 1 1970 GMT.
 * The argument time is in seconds since then.
 * The localtime(t) entry returns a pointer to an array
 * containing
 *
 *  seconds (0-59)
 *  minutes (0-59)
 *  hours (0-23)
 *  day of month (1-31)
